prompts.frontCover: 2D flat illustration of a dreamy fantasy birthday scene for a greeting card. The characters of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo are transformed into whimsical cartoon versions, keeping their clothing and joyful expressions. Jordan is gleefully snowboarding down a river made of flowing soy sauce, dodging playful, floating pieces of wagyu steak and sushi rolls. Lao Lao is close behind him, laughing as she deftly navigates on a snowboard made of a giant Chinese takeout box. The background is a magical, ethereal landscape with snowy mountains made of fluffy white rice under a pastel-colored sky with soft, glowing clouds. Instead of trees, the landscape is dotted with giant, whimsical pieces of broccoli and bok choy. In the sky, glowing binary code (0s and 1s) drifts down gently like snowflakes. In the center of the image, the text "Happy Birthday Jordan" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The overall atmosphere is humorous, magical, and full of imaginative details.
